{"tid":841244,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養龜問題","createTime":"2018-09-29T12:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T08:56:34.000Z","uid":50099,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"07b21878193372e55822241c2c1edc9814a44233","tid":841244,"uid":50099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"呢隻龜 我3歲開始養 養到依家 我都25歲<br />\n5年前有另一隻死左<br />\n得返佢<br />\n我好似覺得佢有問題  唔知係咪浸得耐<br />\n得長期都水過半身 同冇乜機會曬到太陽<br />\n一直都比普通龜糧佢食 係呢幾日先買d 鈣片<br />\n但佢唔會食 等佢溶<br />\n我覺得佢個殻d 色 同埋佢好似好白 仲有d手腳好似浸到甩皮咁 點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/201712_7ce98b71a32e5ba7dbdf0c105631e63d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F201712_7ce98b71a32e5ba7dbdf0c105631e63d.png&h=28ddb71d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/201716_0a58c2050a031f9f6a99aa3c235d9e92.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F201716_0a58c2050a031f9f6a99aa3c235d9e92.png&h=3ccbd4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/201720_c0c0119d8952775e2c5a5fb128606705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F201720_c0c0119d8952775e2c5a5fb128606705.png&h=688ba5ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62990980e8eed78544a056289e5ad53f503d1eb1","tid":841244,"uid":202409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"樓主，水龜一定要浸水過龜殼頂，唔係既話殼會開始反甲。同埋要比佢曬多D太陽。你而家隻龜係唔夠太陽至會咁。鈣分其實唔駛落。如果你嫌水太多，寧願放幾夠磚比佢做陸地，都唔可以少水。如果咁做，隻龜既情況都冇改善，可以試吓落龜精靈加勤換水。畢竟隻龜都耐，如果都係冇改善，咁就RIP。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95ba0bcf58dfeeb61dc777fdff0c58e2339866d","tid":841244,"uid":202409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"最先換咗清水先<img